Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.97,0:37:49.72,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}這是新的任務
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.85,0:37:51.48,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}超越自己吧
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.18,0:37:56.69,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4\3c&H9753DE&}庫特  加油啊  你一定能做到
