Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.98,0:38:00.90,CHS,,0,0,0,,小鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.94,0:38:04.02,CHS,,0,0,0,,來  庫特
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.03,0:38:05.44,CHS,,0,0,0,,任務開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.45,0:38:06.24,CHS,,0,0,0,,是
